&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Education &amp;amp; Experience&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Associate’s degree in Accounting, Finance, or a related field preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3–5 years of direct experience in accounts payable or a similar finance role.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solid understanding of accounts payable principles and best practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency with automated accounting systems and intermediate to advanced Excel skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
