&lt;li&gt;Strong organizational and multitasking abilities to manage competing deadlines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Effective verbal and written communication skills for liaising with vendors and internal teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work independently with minimal supervision while maintaining confidentiality.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
